--- !u!114 &820284197
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 820284195}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 48fdfcc8a67199e4aa51c8e7b7b14715, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::WitcherRightVersion.Dialogue.DialogueInteractable
  displayName: Elder Voytsekh
  interactionPrompt: Talk
  startNodeId: start
  returnToElderNodeId: return
  completedQuestNodeId: completed
  dialogueNodes:
  - Id: start
    SpeakerName: Elder Voytsekh
    Body: Witcher. You came for the notice, then listen well. Something from the
      swamp drags people off the southern road.
    Choices:
    - Text: Tell me about the contract.
      NextNodeId: contract
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: Why blame the swamp so quickly?
      NextNodeId: doubt
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: I will come back later.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
  - Id: contract
    SpeakerName: Elder Voytsekh
    Body: Find the tracks near the reeds, kill the beast, and return with proof.
      Fifty crowns when the road is safe again.
    Choices:
    - Text: I accept the contract.
      NextNodeId: accepted
      FlagToSet: acceptedSwampContract
      QuestAction: start_swamp_contract
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: I need more answers first.
      NextNodeId: doubt
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: Not now.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
  - Id: doubt
    SpeakerName: Elder Voytsekh
    Body: Because I have buried three villagers this month. If you want old stories,
      ask Marta. If you want coin, go south.
    Choices:
    - Text: I accept the contract.
      NextNodeId: accepted
      FlagToSet: acceptedSwampContract
      QuestAction: start_swamp_contract
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: I will speak with Marta first.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
  - Id: accepted
    SpeakerName: Elder Voytsekh
    Body: Good. Start at the muddy road south of the village. And witcher... do not
      stir up fears you cannot put back down.
    Choices:
    - Text: I will find your beast.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
  - Id: return
    SpeakerName: Elder Voytsekh
    Body: You are back. I heard the thing screaming near the reeds. Tell me the road
      is clear.
    Choices:
    - Text: The drowner is dead. Here is your proof.
      NextNodeId: choice_response
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: returned_to_elder
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: Not yet.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
  - Id: choice_response
    SpeakerName: Elder Voytsekh
    Body: Then the village can breathe. The swamp gave us a beast, and you cut it
      down. That is the end of it.
    Choices:
    - Text: The swamp is guilty. Pay me.
      NextNodeId: reward
      FlagToSet: MayorSupported
      QuestAction: accepted_elder_version
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: This is not just a monster. Something is wrong here.
      NextNodeId: warning_after_contract
      FlagToSet: questionedElderVersion
      QuestAction: questioned_elder_version
      ClosesDialogue: 0
  - Id: warning_after_contract
    SpeakerName: Elder Voytsekh
    Body: Careful, witcher. People here need sleep more than old wounds. Take your
      coin and leave buried things buried.
    Choices:
    - Text: I will take the reward. But I am not done looking.
      NextNodeId: reward
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 0
  - Id: reward
    SpeakerName: Elder Voytsekh
    Body: Fifty experience worth of work, twenty crowns, and Marta's antitoxin recipe.
      Spend them quietly.
    Choices:
    - Text: Contract complete.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: swamp_contract_reward_received
      ClosesDialogue: 1
  - Id: completed
    SpeakerName: Elder Voytsekh
    Body: The road is quieter now. Let us hope it stays that way.
    Choices:
    - Text: For now.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
